OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779293476
OL,3,CKent County Council warns of rise in
OL,4,Cfly-tipping
OL,6,FKent County Council is warning of a
OL,7,Frise in fly-tipping and has launched a
OL,8,Fcampaign to keep communities clean.
OL,10,FThe authority says incidents are often
OL,11,Fa result of rogue traders offering to
OL,12,Ftake bulky waste away cheaply, only to
OL,13,Fdump it illegally.
OL,15,FThe campaign, collaborating with local
OL,16,Fcouncils, is running through May and
OL,17,FJune to help residents dispose of
OL,18,Fwaste responsibly.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
