OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779293476
OL,3,CKent County Council warns of rise in
OL,4,Cfly-tipping
OL,6,FIt is encouraging people to "check
OL,7,Fbefore they chuck" - in the hope
OL,8,Fpeople will be empowered with clear
OL,9,Fadvice and easy actions they can take
OL,10,Fwhen arranging for waste to be removed
OL,11,Ffrom their homes.
OL,13,FBy making informed choices, the
OL,14,Fcouncil says the public can help to
OL,15,Fprotect Kent's countryside and
OL,16,Fneighbourhoods.
OL,18,FThe campaign highlights three simple
OL,19,Fsteps to make a difference.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
