OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779293476
OL,3,CKent County Council warns of rise in
OL,4,Cfly-tipping
OL,6,FThe checks aim to help people identify
OL,7,Frogue waste carriers and give them
OL,8,Fconfidence to reject their offers.
OL,10,FAnd the council is reminding people
OL,11,Fthat residents have a duty of care for
OL,12,Ftheir waste, even when handing it to
OL,13,Fsomeone else.
OL,15,FThe campaign is also signposting
OL,16,Fresidents to a range of responsible
OL,17,Fdisposal options. These include
OL,18,Frecycling centres, local district and
OL,19,Fborough council bulky waste
OL,20,Fcollections and local charities that
OL,21,Fcan reuse or repurpose unwanted items.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
