OL,3,CKent County Council warns of rise in
OL,4,Cfly-tipping
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FCabinet Member for Environment,
OL,12,FCoastal Regeneration and Public
OL,13,FHealth, Jamie Henderson, said: "Kent's
OL,14,Fcountryside is something we are all
OL,15,Fproud of, and most people want to keep
OL,16,Fit that way.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
