OL,3,CKent County Council warns of rise in
OL,4,Cfly-tipping
OL,6,F"Unfortunately, fly-tipping is
OL,7,Fincreasing, often as a result of rogue
OL,8,Ftraders offering to take bulky waste
OL,9,Faway cheaply, only to dump it
OL,10,Fillegally.
OL,12,F"This campaign is about making it
OL,13,Feasier for everyone to take simple
OL,14,Fsteps that protect both themselves and
OL,15,Fthe environment.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
